  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>Clone</TypeRef> method creates another owning module handle for the same loaded module.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[IModuleHandle::unique_ptr Clone() const;]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="IModuleHandle!cobalt.graphics.IModuleHandle">
        A new module handle object referencing the same loaded module.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
